		<div class="comment-author vcard">
		<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/13d0d197e098346f75f94af67ef8267c?s=55&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D55&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-55 photo' height='55' width='55' />		<span class="authorname">Neno Brown</span>
