		<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/ed5214d4b49154ba0dc397a28ee90eb7?s=55&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D55&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-55 photo' height='55' width='55' />		<span class="authorname">Richard M Stallman</span>
